# TrendWeave AI
A simple AI-powered fashion design intelligence platform.
this project uses groq ai api for ai integration
It analyzes trends, demographics, season, and regional context.
The system generates fashion design ideas with fabric suggestions.
It also provides sizing recommendations and production feasibility insights.
Users can explore designs through a clean and modern interface.
The app includes reference images for visual inspiration.
It is built using Python and Streamlit.
## Live Link:
(https://trendwave-ai-sfvdfbnuptju7vsn9udsjw.streamlit.app/)
